Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:24.82,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:29.29,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:31.29,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.63,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.55,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:44.47,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:50.27,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:56.19,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:58.86,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:03.36,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:07.08,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.87,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:14.75,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:17.59,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:26.85,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:29.93,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.73,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
