Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:56.21,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko, how about openin' the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:01:59.39,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.93,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.68,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Huh? Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:14.94,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.78,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I love the cakes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.28,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.87,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah. This is Jun's family's shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.33,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh... I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.12,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.79,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,If you'd like, why don't you come over to my place and watch them practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.89,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's over. She hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.72,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What's that, avant-garde?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.89,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Come on, Richie. Get your head on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.27,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,How we gonna have a session?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.65,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Everyone, Yurika is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:03:00.57,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Ri, didn't your dad tell you that outsiders aren't allowed down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:06.66,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika's our friend, so I'm\Nsure Dad won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.66,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Well, Yurika, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.50,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.75,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm just going to get a little fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.42,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.56,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.56,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,It's Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:40.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're Sentaro's sister... Sachiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you playing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.74,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah. All my friends are off at cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Then how about we play together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:52.75,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.88,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.59,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,It's not playing? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:06.09,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,That thing's a relic, so sometimes it gets ornery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.85,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,You just gotta work a little magic on it when it gets like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.61,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wow, Jun. How'd that get it to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:19.90,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:24.24,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Hello, is this the Children's \NTelephone Counseling Office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.07,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:32.62,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,You see, there's this boy named Hashiguchi who's always mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:36.12,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,He hides my slippers, pulls my hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.63,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,What do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:48.01,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You know, maybe that Hashiguchi actually likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.38,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,My guess is he wants to be friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but he doesn't know how to express his feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.86,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,so he acts out like that without \Nreally thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.94,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,He does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:06.45,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Recently, I made the girl that I really like cry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I want to apologize to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but even if I do, I don't think she'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.66,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.67,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,That was my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.85,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's no good. I can't stay mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.52,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.90,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.15,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,Coincidentally, I've been going to the shop for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:49.07,apollon main,Yurika,0,0,0,,I had no idea it was your family's.
