Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.29,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,The coincidences keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.37,apollon main,Jun,0,0,0,,Even the name is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.76,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Actually, there's someone that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:12.22,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He's the only one I can think of right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.64,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm flattered by the way you feel about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.68,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm flattered, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.37,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.29,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,H-Hi. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.08,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You seem kinda troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.00,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Here, eat this an' cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.50,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.17,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I said something terrible to Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:53.22,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He might not come back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.94,apollon main,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.19,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.90,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.78,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,know who it is that Ri'ko li...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.03,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.28,apollon main,Taichi,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.28,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.83,apollon main,Kota,0,0,0,,School starts again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.75,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I-I can't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:24.46,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,It's impossible to talk about anything romantic in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.96,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! It's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.18,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come over for practice during winter vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:44.31,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... The teacher told me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.58,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Dad's finally come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but everything seems so bleak right now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.09,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,that I can't bring myself to talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.85,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen—What are you doing out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.85,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie! Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.53,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, put a jacket on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.20,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,We're gonna practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:37.74,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:43.12,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko's lonely without you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.62,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Come on, all you gotta do is stop by the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.58,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not going back there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.92,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.18,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Kaoru, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.26,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,I thought I heard a loud noise in here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.68,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.39,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:09.73,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wanted to give you this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.40,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,It's from Shizu, our old housekeeper, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Shizu? Oh, that takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.28,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,She wrote about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:26.00,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,We've had our problems over the years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.67,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,but it seems she happened to run into your mother in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:34.42,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,She got your mother's address and insisted I pass it on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.80,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,We split up when you were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:41.18,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,so you might not remember her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:47.18,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,But if you'd like to see her, then maybe you could go on your next break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.44,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,I know this is sudden and may leave you at a loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.86,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,but whether you go or not is totally up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:57.90,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let you get back to your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:04.62,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie. You can take her some sweet rice treats as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I never said I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:09.87,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You're not goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm just not up to it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.21,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:19.68,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You'll regret it for the rest of your life if you pass up this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.27,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.35,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:30.39,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,What are you doing? I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.37,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, you're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.55,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Blue trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:01.97,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,"Blue train" refers to the limited express trains from Asakaze
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.55,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,that have dedicated blue sleeper cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.06,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Did you know that the design of the \Nfront and back car are different
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.69,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,because they have to switch between being the lead car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:24.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, this is my\Nfirst time traveling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.62,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is it like a trip to help me get over my heartache?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.83,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey! You're late, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:36.13,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Y'know, it's a good thing I asked Maruo to get me a ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:42.72,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I felt like takin' a trip to \NTokyo too, so I'm taggin' along!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:52.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I only went on this trip so I could be alone and think things over quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:56.90,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Man, travel an' frozen tangerines go together like bread an' butter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.36,apollon main,Old Woman,0,0,0,,I do have one more tangerine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.48,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, much obliged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:04.07,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,They taste better before they thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Damn that Maruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,By the way, how can you afford this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.92,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, I have money saved up from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.04,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,And then I sold some old records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.30,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You don't have nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:24.47,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, if I can make it to Jun's place,\NI'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.68,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What a airheaded fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.23,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Here, this is yours, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.23,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko said the food in the dining car would probably be expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.11,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,so she made these for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.95,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ain't you gonna eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.74,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,She's been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.89,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with all these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.40,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Is there a festival? Or a New Year's sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Tokyo Station is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why don't you go sightseeing around Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.49,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I wanna see what your mom's like,\Nso I'm comin' with you.
