Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.46,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.75\shad0\bord0\i1\fs35\frx2\fry0\pos(635,88)\c&H344235&}Blue Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:38.62,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck? This is some workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.13,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait, maybe I got the address wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.84,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, let's go in an' ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.18,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind about meeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.89,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.72,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What are you talkin' about?\NYou've come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.68,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's better if I don't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.02,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Even if I did, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.52,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.12,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,She said it's your mom's day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:15.74,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Said she'd meet you here tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.16,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,So we'll come back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:22.33,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,All right, I say we relax at Jun's place until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.59,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Do you two have business with Katsuragi Junichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:33.01,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.97,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,There's no point in waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.43,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,He's been missing since last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.48,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.27,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:45.36,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it he got in bad with some faction, and now he's in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:49.70,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,It's possible that he's just shacking up with some girl, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.66,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\frz41.041\pos(586,307)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.66,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\pos(994,444)\frz71.121\clip(m 1025 377 l 985 356 930 525 1012 538)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.66,apollon main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H010209&\shad0\bord0\fs30\blur0.75\fnOld newspaper font\b0\pos(830,448)\frz62.54\clip(m 865 389 l 770 472 753 530 824 546)}Fukahori Yurika
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.66,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,That guy's popular with the college girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:56.20,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, that doesn't surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.58,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Right, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.66,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:03.79,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Have you two come all the way from Kyushu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:11.38,apollon main,Hasegawa,0,0,0,,Well, let's make our guests from faraway Kyushu feel welcome! {too lazy to make this not sound terrible}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.51,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,With shochu and water...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.51,apollon main,All,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.02,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:18.93,apollon main,Hasegawa,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right! You wouldn't \Nbelieve how stupid this guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:31.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's always in some kind of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:35.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,When I'm with him, his stupidity rubs off on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.29,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Good for you. You're lucky \Nto have such a good buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Buddy? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.17,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,The best kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.30,apollon main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty rare to have a friend you can get goofy with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.84,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Treasure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:53.01,apollon main,Okada,0,0,0,,Unlike love affairs, friendship is for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.91,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.99,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,You're Kaoru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.41,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Idiot! What are you standing around like a scarecrow for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.25,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.75,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry up and come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.97,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I've never eaten curry this fancy before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.14,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Go on. Don't be shy. Just eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.10,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.98,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.39,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,I like the way you shovel it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:48.73,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,I've got a thing for men with a hearty appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She's totally different from how I imagined her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.70,apollon main,Kaoru and Mom,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.70,apollon 2nd,Kaoru and Mom,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.37,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.50,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Mother and son in perfect unison!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.75,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry. He has no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.88,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Is he a friend from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:14.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah. Or more like, we play music together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.09,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He's a drummer, and I play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:17.93,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.06,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, you used to love it when your dad played the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.18,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,He would play, and I'd sing along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:30.94,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Even if you were crying, you'd always stop and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:35.44,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,That's such a happy memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:39.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I don't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Anyway, Dad never likes to talk about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.50,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Of course he doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.83,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Who would want to talk about \Na washout of a mother like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.55,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Looks like the rain's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.18,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a little stroll around Ginza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.35,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,I think he wanted to give us some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.68,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Better eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.62,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,It's this curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.45,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,It's spicier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.46,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.67,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,By the way, how's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.38,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.75,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Have your eyes on any girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.09,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, did it not work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:41.76,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Mom, I'd rather not talk about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:44.05,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,What, I'm right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.52,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wh-What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.52,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Well, just the idea of the baby boy in my memory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.77,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,who'd call me "Mama" and make gurgling noises... having a broken heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.07,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,You're in the heyday of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.53,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,A broken heart! Not bad, not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm lovelorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.21,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,The more I laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.42,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,the more whatever had been building up inside me disappeared into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.13,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,My mind emptied out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.43,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.39,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't gonna make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.52,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Mom, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.31,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's a jazz record.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.23,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's a song called "Lullaby of Birdland."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.03,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Listen and then try singing along to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.24,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll come back to visit you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.61,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,so until then, I'd like you to practice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.24,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,But this is in English, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.08,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,I don't know English at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:52.46,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. Just imitate what you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:56.67,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Jazz sounds best when it's sung by a woman with a husky voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll come back for sure, so practice for me, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.76,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Kaoru... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.85,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:13.27,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,I thought... I'd probably never see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.77,apollon main,Mom,0,0,0,,That's what I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:32.04,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why did my mom leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:39.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Those words that I couldn't ask flew away somewhere with this scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:44.47,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Mom's mouth formed the words, "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:50.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I shook my head, but I'm not sure she saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.10,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.19,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,That was heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.07,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.86,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Where were ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Ri.
